How to use 

LaTeX classes
- ~/texmf/tex/latex/
- run 
  texhash ~/texmf

LyX layouts
- rename original source to different name, e.g. add .src suffix
- symlink them into ~/.lyx/layouts/ with original name
- reconfigure in LyX


LyX fonts
- apt-get install texlive-xetex
- reconfigure in LyX
- view PDF (XeTeX)
